profile:
We are a Calgary Area Drywall Company, with over 16 years experience in the drywall field. We offer a professional drywall services and have played a major role in many notable projects. As a company we focus on being cutting edge in our trade.  Using the best materials for the job and practicing the most modern techniques, we execute our projects by paying close attention to management details for example;
 -Insight to prevent delays
-Putting up dust barriers
-Correspondence with our customers

At Finishing touch we use both in house and sub trades. We assure our workmanship is of high quality.
name: Finishing Touch Drywall
